data.description: Perfect retirement home! Separate living room from family room and kitchen. Kitchen and dining area newly renovated with added squ.ft to the back. Granite countertops with a large island and plenty of cabinets make this kitchen perfect for gathering friends and family around. Nice sized bedrooms with their own bathrooms. The secondary bathroom was beautifully remodeled for wheenchair access. This home also has an open room that can be a hobby room or a den. Back patio has a screened in Arizona room for enjoying those beautiful sunsets. The large lot boasts over 10,000 squ. ft and is fully landscaped with mature citrus trees and low maintenance desert landscape design.
